description: The Deka Euro Prime ESG UCITS ETF is a UCITS IV-compliant mutual fund that replicates the performance of the Solactive Euro Prime ESG Index (price index). The index tracks the performance of the 30 largest Eurozone companies that have a Prime Status rating according to the ISS-ESG rating (assessment of companies from a social and environmental perspective) and are not excluded by the defined exclusion criteria.
name: Deka Euro Prime ESG UCITS ETF
